h2 DATIVE CASE
p
	| In a sentence the Dative case often indicates an indirect object: a person or object to whom the action is directed.
ul
	li Позвони мне!
	li Скажи мне!
	li Дай мне!
p In the Dative case nouns and pronouns answer the questions: To whom? To what?
p
